    "body": "The following improvements of the prototype driver code in `cmd/state/stateless.go` can be done:\r\n\r\nThe `return` statement needs to be added after this line:\r\nhttps://github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/blob/21c981eb84e5543d2426c794568d37b23ec82831/cmd/state/stateless.go#L282\r\nso that we keep the correct state file just before the block with invalid processing, for more efficient debugging\r\n\r\nThe deferred committing and closing of the database:\r\nhttps://github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/blob/21c981eb84e5543d2426c794568d37b23ec82831/cmd/state/stateless.go#L157\r\nneeds to capture `blockNum` and output instruction to resume the run, like this one:\r\nhttps://github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/blob/21c981eb84e5543d2426c794568d37b23ec82831/cmd/state/stateless.go#L315",
